"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-british-star-calls-andy-murray-a-cry-baby-paris-olympics-2024-21337466\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"British tennis star Liam Broady has playfully calledAndy Murraya 'cry baby' after the 37-year-old broke down in tears at theParisOlympics on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7408277204144864, \"rank\": 0.33582571299858316, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 20, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Broady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Liam Broady\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Broady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Broady\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Broady and Murray are close and regularly tease another acrosssocial mediawith the former spotting a golden opportunity to wind up his friend on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 162, \"end\": 168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9563329639713756e-20, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old walked past a screen showing highlights fromMurray's second-round men's doubles winat Roland-Garros, which took place on Tuesday night.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 459, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Broady took a picture of the screen the moment Murraywas seen sobbing in his chairas the victory was confirmed, posting it with the caption: 'What a cry baby.'\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He signed off his X post with a smirking face emoji, in a sign that the interaction was just another bit of fun between the duo and certainly not anything malicious.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's unbelievably emotional,' Murray said after he and Dan Evans booked their spot in the quarter-finals of the men's doubles on the Roland-Garros clay courts to once again slam the brakes on his upcoming retirement.\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9563329639713756e-20, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"score\": 0.835626095867947, \"rank\": 0.19670748052617462, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You are obviously unbelievably happy and then for whatever reason, you have got happy tears I do not know why that's the case.\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a cry baby.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u008fpic.twitter.com/pmnZWBBO0w  'I was really emotional at the end of the match - extremely happy, excited that we managed to get through with another amazing finish.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It takes a lot out of you so I am glad we get a day off tomorrow.'\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Broady and Murray have been trying to one-up each other on social media for a while now, very much to the amusement of tennis fans.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1400, \"end\": 1406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9563329639713756e-20, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, a grumpy Broady posted: 'First match at 10am today so have to warm up at 8:30.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Breakfast does not open till 9am?\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Walked into player area and we have got\\u2026 bagels.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Really good for a high standard of tennis and tennis tournament in Atlanta.'\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999993259202709, \"rank\": 5.263885949882158e-07, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray replied: 'Hope you are ok mate.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9563329639713756e-20, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That sounds terrible.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Surprised you had not checked the breakfast situation ahead of time like most professionals would have done.'\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Broady then wrote back: 'You have five people just to wipe your bum for you man you have never checked a situation ahead of time in your life.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not the same!'\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Scary moment gymnast goes flying after 'equipment malfunction' in Olympics final  ArrowMORE:Team GB star Tommy Fleetwood 'heartbroken' by knife attacks in hometown of Southport  ArrowMORE:Olympics commentator wants to look away after 'tragic' moment for Brazil legend  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2288, \"end\": 2297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.99980520265444, \"rank\": 0.0001948352962102313, \"text\": \"Southport\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2375, \"end\": 2381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995492820125045, \"rank\": 0.00044902383846401203, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2696, \"end\": 2702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource